modules.name: Ceder 7672
modules.notes:
By Michael and Heather Haworth.
This Wind in the Face get-out can be used when teaching the concept of "Leaders" to your dancers. After the second Wheel & Deal, dancers are not used to hearing the term "Leaders". The term "Centers" is more often used, or a designating term is dropped all together since some callers will argue that the only legal "Pass Thru" must happen in the center. Therefore centers are active.
